title: Red Dwarf Tongue Tied 1993 The Cat
description:
In season 2 of Red Dwarf Episode 6 'Parallel Universe' The cat had a dream sequence, where he and the rest of Red Dwarf sang the song 'Tongue Tied'. Due to popular demand from the Red Dwarf Fan Club, this was released in 1993 in single, 12 inch and CD form. Also released was a VHS video entitled 'The Making Of Tongue Tied' with exclusive video scenes, and directed by Danny John-Jules. This torrent includes all the available material from then, including items which were no longer available when re-released in 2013.
